約至2021年，英媒稱，利物浦在過去六週與薩爾斯堡進行了友好的對話。<br />\n  在薩爾斯堡紅牛從歐聯出局後，紅軍本週迅速採取了行動，以避開了德甲和意甲球會等的競爭，當中包括慕遜加柏和AC米蘭。<br />\n  英媒稱，曼聯原本將南野拓實視為麥迪遜的替代者，並連續關注了日本國腳幾個月。但由於南野拓實合約中的解約條款，利物浦在競爭中獲得了優勢。<br />\n  南野拓實現年24歲，代表日本國家隊出戰22場比賽攻入11球，在最近的四場世盃外他攻入了5球。<br />\n  南野拓實將在接下來的幾週接受體檢，並商談個人條款。據悉，南野拓實對利物浦的興趣感到很榮幸，並已準備簽約。"},{"pid":"d9beba2c664cd5cd4a8920d0dababffdea48f987","tid":1781343,"uid":50740,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:48:53.000Z","msg":"go mu la diu"},{"pid":"117af1083e39fe7ccf402dd46a90e8fc6d6ee445","tid":1781343,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c50d418467c7611494aa0cbb23dc003acdb69b0","tid":1781343,"uid":5649,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:42:12.000Z","msg":"過黎撐鏝，我地名宿係支那人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:50:55.000Z","msg":"牙海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6124f7b8ca4fc3c8cec54d84bd580f1f552a1c14","tid":1781343,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c50d418467c7611494aa0cbb23dc003acdb69b0","tid":1781343,"uid":5649,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:42:12.000Z","msg":"過黎撐鏝，我地名宿係支那人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e8ee41a9b3965ccf94c8d1f04b662a10026f2f","tid":1781343,"uid":34934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"117af1083e39fe7ccf402dd46a90e8fc6d6ee445","tid":1781343,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c50d418467c7611494aa0cbb23dc003acdb69b0","tid":1781343,"uid":5649,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:42:12.000Z","msg":"過黎撐鏝，我地名宿係支那人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:50:55.000Z","msg":"牙海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face